%^BOLD%^-=%^RED%^Suffering Domain%^BOLD%^%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

Clerics who choose the suffering domain thrive upon inflicting 
pain on others, and sometimes even having it inflicted upon 
themselves. The domain grants access to spells that harness 
the very essence of agony itself, using it to damage and 
weaken opponents.

The suffering domain contains the following spells:
Body Blades (2nd), Kiss of Torment (5th), Wave of Pain (7th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lord Shadow

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     